<li>Your father's kindness and generosity will be deeply missed.</li>
<li>Please accept my heartfelt sympathy. May his memory be a blessing.</li>
<li>I'm so sorry for your loss. Your father was a truly special person.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort during this difficult time.</li>
<li>May the love and memories you shared bring you some solace.</li>
