<li>Your father's legacy will live on through the many lives he touched.</li>
<li>My thoughts are with you and your family.</li>
<li>Sending love and prayers during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, may his soul rest in peace.</li>
<li>Please know that I'm here for you, whatever you need.</li>
<li>May the memories of your father bring you peace and comfort.</li>
    

